eview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=collapsible%20fabric%20ones&amp;short_url=KKN18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">可折叠的布质衣服</a>（六个，售价 16.99 美元）是我的最爱，因为它们让一切看起来都很整洁，即使里面的东西也很整洁。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/home/my-favorite-household-organizational-items<dc:creator>林赛·埃勒夫森</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Cleaning & Organizing]]></category></item></channel></rss>